OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and sunny day with
OL,6,Fjust a little patchy cloud around for
OL,7,Fsome places in the morning. Feeling
OL,8,Fwarm or very warm, with temperatures
OL,9,Fon the rise.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and settled evening
OL,12,Fwith clear skies across the whole
OL,13,Fregion. Winds will be light and
OL,14,Fvariable but breezy along the coasts.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FSettled and dry day, with
OL,17,Fbright sunshine and light winds.
OL,18,FFeeling hot, though temperatures could
OL,19,Fbe a degree or two cooler along the
OL,20,Fcoast in any sea breezes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
