OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTemperatures starting to reduce on
OL,7,FTuesday and Wednesday as the wind
OL,8,Fturns onshore. Staying mostly dry with
OL,9,Fvariable amounts of cloud. Thursday
OL,10,Flooking cloudy with the chance of a
OL,11,Fshower.
